<div id="checklist-container" class="card bg-light mb-3">
    <div class="card-header">
        Hold your horses! ...and canines, felines, birds, etc. Hold all of them.
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">
            <strong class="text-danger">Don't get scammed!</strong> Fursuit stuff isn't cheap, and you don't want to lose the precious money you've been saving
        </h5>

        <p class="card-text">
            This tool serves for finding a maker/<wbr>studio which will best match your expectations. It can save
            you some time searching. What it can't do for you - <strong>which means you must do that
                yourself</strong> - is to verify the legitimacy of the maker/<wbr>studio you want to commission.
        </p>

        <p class="card-text">
            The <a href="{{ path('should_know') }}">What you should know</a> page contains some helpful information, tips, and links to external resources. It includes a <em>Learn about <strong>the risk</strong></em> {# grep-learn-about-the-risk #} section. <span class="text-danger">You will most probably not get your fursuit in the next weeks, so reading a bit will not hurt.</span>
        </p>

        <div class="card-text">
            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="checklist-ill-be-careful" />
                <label class="form-check-label" for="checklist-ill-be-careful">
                    I'll be careful, I promise! I acknowledge the aforementioned page availability, with all its resources and links.
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-text" id="checklist-age-container">
            <hr />

            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="checklistIsAdult" id="aasImNotAdult" value="NO" />
                <label class="form-check-label" for="aasImNotAdult">
                    I am under 18 years old, and I need a maker who accepts commissions from underage people.
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="checklistIsAdult" id="aasImAdult" value="YES" />
                <label class="form-check-label" for="aasImAdult">
                    I am at least 18 years old. I agree that lying about my age would be a stupid idea with consequences, up to getting banned from commissioning my beloved fursuit maker, ever.
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-text" id="checklist-wants-sfw-container">
            <hr />

            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="checklistWantsSfw" id="aasKeepSfw" value="YES" />
                <label class="form-check-label" for="aasKeepSfw">
                    Even though I am an adult, I prefer my experience to remain 100% SFW.
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="checklistWantsSfw" id="aasAllowNsfw" value="NO" />
                <label class="form-check-label" for="aasAllowNsfw">
                    I may not be interested in such, but I don't mind running into NSFW stuff on some websites.
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-text">
            <hr />

            <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="checklist-i-like-buttons" />
                <label class="form-check-label" for="checklist-i-like-buttons">
                    I like clicking buttons (optional)
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="card-text text-end">
            <input type="button" id="checklist-dismiss-btn" class="btn" value="" />
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
